cs.HC, cs.LG, cs.CY, cs.CE, cs.SI

This paper discusses the application of machine learning in healthcare, specifically in promoting healthy lifestyles and preventing chronic diseases. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction). The paper also discusses the interactive machine learning process, which suggests a focus on machine learning algorithms and techniques, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. The use of a telemedicine system and digital implementation suggests a focus on computer networks and communications, making cs.CY (Computers and Society) a possible category. The focus on promoting healthy lifestyles and preventing chronic diseases suggests a focus on biomedical engineering, making cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science) a possible category. Finally, the use of personalized interventions suggests a focus on personalized medicine, making cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) a possible category.
